00:01:28.230 --> 00:01:32.670
deliberately. Time lies in the world and

00:01:32.670 --> 00:01:35.490
waits for the spring waters to bring its

00:01:35.490 --> 00:01:38.520
body to the surface. For this spring

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:41.820
waters do not come. Because time does

00:01:41.820 --> 00:01:45.090
not exist anymore. And there is no

00:01:45.090 --> 00:01:48.935
spring and there is no water to come.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:53.165
And there is no sun to rise and set.

00:01:53.190 --> 00:01:57.150
There is endless February and we're all

00:01:57.150 --> 00:02:00.750
